<doc id="790048" url="https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=790048" title="Pyropeltidae">
Pyropeltidae

Pyropeltidae là một Họ of gastropods in the clade Vetigastropoda (according taxonomy of the Gastropoda by Bouchet & Rocroi, 2005).

This family has no subfamilies.

Their habitat include hydrothermal vents and whale-fall habitats.

